title: War of the Roses: She Crawled Through His Doggy Door
description: Becca saw that her boyfriend Chris was getting texts from his ex so she asked him about it and he said the typical guy thing, "She's Crazy."  The thing is, she sort of is because of what she did to his fish when they used to date.  But is she being crazy texting him or is Chris still seeing her?
